{"tid":2023423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本雜誌以東奧會徽與病毒融合圖案作封面 東京奧組委要求撤回","createTime":"2020-05-19T04:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T04:37:06.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d20252aa009003305aa8e6c1eb340849df6e5b43","tid":2023423,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"雜誌以東奧會徽與病毒融合圖案作封面 東京奧組委要求撤回<br />\n19.05.2020 08:54<br />\n<br />\n駐日外國記者協會出版的4月號雜誌封面，刊出把「東京奧運會徽」與「病毒形狀」融合的圖案，並在下面標註代表新型冠狀病毒的英文字樣「COVID-19」。共同社報道，東京奧組委要求駐日外國記者協會，撤回有關的封面設計。<br />\n<br />\n有關雜誌為《NUMBER 1 SHIMBUN》，協會網站上仍能下載涉事的4月號。奧組委表示，新型冠狀病毒在對生命、經濟和生活帶來嚴重危害，刊載病毒與會徽關聯的設計，令人感到遺憾，又認為做法侵犯著作權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAUY4tZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAUY4tZ.jpg&h=c1558398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288421&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288421%26csid%3D261_367&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2FzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=23515f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288421&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"28376c092b62cea228d263f4f0a3142361c4e4ee","tid":2023423,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"傷害一億三千萬日本人的感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}